      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I’m Nobody! Who are you? Are you – Nobody – too? Then there’s a pair of us!&lt;/em&gt; ~ Emily Dickinson&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hello, stranger!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My name is Boudhayan Bhattacharya but I usually go by the alias &lt;em&gt;bbhtt&lt;/em&gt; online.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I completed my Bachelors (Honours) in Mathematics in June 2021 and
Masters in Mathematics in June 2023. I&amp;rsquo;m currently doing Ph.D. in
Mathematical Biology. I teach and sometimes contribute to various &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Free_and_open-source_software&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;FOSS&lt;/a&gt;
projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I like watching movies and TV, reading books and listening to music.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I play online chess sometimes, although I never studied it seriously. I want to though, someday!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a place for random things in life that I find interesting.&lt;/p&gt;
